Recruitment Features:
    • Applications:
        ◦ Manage and track job applications, degrees, refuse reasons, and tags.
    • Activities:
        ◦ Define different activities related to recruitment.
    • Activity Types:
        ◦ Categorize activities with different types.
    • Employees:
        ◦ Configure employee details related to recruitment.
    • Departments:
        ◦ Define different departments for recruitment purposes.
    • Job Positions:
        ◦ Specify different job positions.
    • Employment Types:
        ◦ Define different types of employment.
    • Job Positions Stages:
        ◦ Define stages for job positions.
    • UTMs:
        ◦ Configure and manage UTM parameters for recruitment.
    • Reporting:
        ◦ Generate reports related to recruitment analysis.
